2 10 10 1 2 Special Abilities: Quermians begin the game with one rank in Perception.  They still may not train Perception above rank 2 during character creation.

Additional Limbs: Quermians have six lims: two legs and four arms.  As a result, they gain an additional free maneuver per turn, although they still may not perform more than 2 maneuvers per turn.
